that LME/MCO. Copies of outpatient commitment orders sent by the clerk of
court to an outpatient treatment center or physician under this section,
including orders sent to an LME/MCO, shall be sent by the most reliable and
expeditious means, but in no event less than 48 hours after the hearing.within
